examples.en: She hummed a melody.
The refrigerator is humming.
Bees cluster and hum.
The square was humming with activity.
The restaurant hums on weekends.
examples.ru: По выходным в этом ресторане очень людно и шумно.

examples.en: The room was humming with the voices of a large number of guests.
examples.ru: Комната гудела от голосов многочисленных гостей.

examples.en: I hardly need to tell you that he's not quite the man to make things hum.
examples.ru: Едва ли нужно говорить, что он не тот человек, у которого работа кипит.

examples.en: He began to hum a tune.
The streets were humming with life.
We hummed along to the music.
There is a constant hum of military preparation.
I was humming to myself.
By noon, the office was really humming.
examples.ru: К полудню в конторе уже полным ходом шла работа.

examples.en: I hummed a little song.
The garden was humming with bees.
The speciality of the hum is the lone drunk.
examples.ru: Занятие постоянно занимающего деньги - одиночные запои.

examples.en: The refrigerator hummed in the background.
By nine o'clock, the restaurant was humming.
examples.ru: К девяти часам ресторан уже гудел вовсю.

examples.en: Machines hummed on the factory floor.
Tony was humming to himself as he drove along.
examples.ru: Тони что-то напевал себе под нос, пока ехал дальше.
